<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.3.9">
<l>karumukil pōlvatōr mēṉi kaiyaṉa vāḻiyuñ caṅkum</l>
<l>peruviṟal vāṉavar cūḻa vēḻula kuntoḻu tētta</l>
<l>orumaka ḷāyarma ṭantai yoruttini lamakaḷ maṟṟait</l>
<l>tirumaka ḷōṭumva ruvāṉ cittira kūṭattuḷ ḷāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He who appeared with one girl – a herder maid, one woman - lady earth,</l>
<l>[And] the other - lady Tiru, that which is like a dark cloud – [his] body,</l>
<l>The things of [his] hands - the conch and disc, as powerful celestials circled,</l>
<l>As the seven worlds praised and adored [him],</l>
<l rend="indent">he is the one present in Citrakūṭam.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
